'''溴化铟''' (三溴化铟)，化学式 InBr<sub>3</sub>，是一种无机化合物，由[[铟|铟]]和[[溴|溴]]组成。它是一种[[路易斯酸|路易斯酸]]，用于有机合成。<ref name="ThirupathiKim2009">{{cite journal|last1=Thirupathi|first1=Ponnaboina|last2=Kim|first2=Sung Soo|title=InBr3: A Versatile Catalyst for the Different Types of Friedel−Crafts Reactions|journal=The Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume=74|issue=20|year=2009|pages=7755–7761|issn=0022-3263|doi=10.1021/jo9014613|pmid=19813765}}</ref>

==结构==
它具有和[[氯化铝|氯化铝]]一样的结构，有六配位的铟原子。<ref name = "indium encyclo">"Indium: Inorganic chemistry", D.G Tuck, ''Encyclopedia of Inorganic Chemistry'' Editor R Bruce King (1994) John Wiley and Sons {{ISBN|0-471-93620-0}}</ref>当熔融时，它的结构是二聚体In<sub>2</sub>Br<sub>6</sub>，并且在气相中主要也是二聚体。溴化铟二聚体具有与[[氯化铝|氯化铝]]二聚体 Al<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>6</sub>有相似结构的桥连溴原子。<ref name = "indium encyclo"/>

==制备和反应==
溴化铟可以由溴和铟直接化合而成。<ref name = "Wiberg&Holleman">Egon Wiberg, Arnold Frederick Holleman (2001) ''Inorganic Chemistry'', Elsevier {{ISBN|0123526515}}</ref>
InBr<sub>3</sub> 可以和[[配体|配体]]（以L显示）形成加合物： InBr<sub>3</sub>L，InBr<sub>3</sub>L<sub>2</sub>和 InBr<sub>3</sub>L<sub>3</sub>。<ref name = "indium encyclo"/>

溴化铟和金属铟反应会产生[[低卤化物|低溴化物]]如：InBr<sub>2</sub>、In<sub>4</sub>Br<sub>7</sub>、In<sub>2</sub>Br<sub>3</sub>、In<sub>5</sub>Br<sub>7</sub>、 In<sub>7</sub>Br<sub>9</sub>和[[一溴化铟|InBr]]<ref name="StaffelMeyer1987">{{cite journal|last1=Staffel|first1=Thomas|last2=Meyer|first2=Gerd|title=The mono-, sesqui-, and dibromides of indium: InBr, In2Br3, and InBr2|journal=Zeitschrift für anorganische und allgemeine Chemie|volume=552|issue=9|year=1987|pages=113–122|issn=0044-2313|doi=10.1002/zaac.19875520913}}</ref><ref name="RuckBärnighausen1999">{{cite journal|last1=Ruck|first1=Michael|last2=Bärnighausen|first2=Hartmut|title=Zur Polymorphie von In5Br7|journal=Zeitschrift für anorganische und allgemeine Chemie|volume=625|issue=4|year=1999|pages=577–585|issn=0044-2313|doi=10.1002/(SICI)1521-3749(199904)625:4<577::AID-ZAAC577>3.0.CO;2-B}}</ref><ref name="Dronskowski1995">{{cite journal|last1=Dronskowski|first1=R.|title=The crystal structure of In7Br9|journal=Zeitschrift für Kristallographie|volume=210|issue=12|year=1995|pages=920–923|issn=0044-2968|doi=10.1524/zkri.1995.210.12.920}}</ref><ref name="StephensonMellor1950">{{cite journal|last1=Stephenson|first1=NC|last2=Mellor|first2=DP|title=The Crystal Structure of Indium Monobromide|journal=Australian Journal of Chemistry|volume=3|issue=4|year=1950|pages=581|issn=0004-9425|doi=10.1071/CH9500581}}</ref>
在回流的二甲苯溶液中，InBr<sub>3</sub>和In金属反应形成InBr<sub>2</sub>。<ref name="FreelandTuck1976">{{cite journal|last1=Freeland|first1=B. H.|last2=Tuck|first2=D. G.|title=Facile synthesis of the lower halides of indium|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=15|issue=2|year=1976|pages=475–476|issn=0020-1669|doi=10.1021/ic50156a050}}</ref>

